If you are expecting someone to send you a personal tell everytime and thank you for a job well done, then try keeping quiet and doing the job you signed up to do without any complaints or hasseling anyone on the raid.  Ohh and attend more than just one cause it really makes you look bad the first time you show up and expect to get more than someone that has been doing it many many times.<br>
