<br>
He was in my guild before and after this CoM raid, when I had not seen these posts. I can say that he is no longer with us now. This wasn't the only reason either, as he gravely insulted the honor of my wife, Renlaieli. Shortly after this, he then raided the plane of his own diety, Tunare. This lack of respect to his god, his officers, and now his raid leaders simply abhors me. He might be a generous man (he is, he has given many expensive items to lower guildees), but this does not make up for these occurrences. <br>
<br>
Lothor -- you simply must learn patience and respect to succeed. I bid you luck in your future, but you have no place in the Bane of Ruin any longer.<br>
<br>
Zrotharr Wrathfist, Judicator of the Bane of Ruin<br>
Mystic of the 54th Winter <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm59.showMessageRange?topicID=430.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm59.showMessageRange?topicID=430.topic&start=41&stop=45>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm59.showPrevMessage?topicID=430.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm59.showNextMessage?topicID=430.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm59.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=430.topic&index=40><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm59.threadControl?topicID=430.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm59.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=430.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm59.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=430.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub94.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspaci